621
00:41:07,490 --> 00:41:12,590
When you're down, I just wanna be there with you.

622
00:41:12,590 --> 00:41:16,300
And I've been calling you,
but you never picked up.

623
00:41:16,300 --> 00:41:21,658
Seeing you okay now means everything.

624
00:41:24,888 --> 00:41:26,838
Say that again.

625
00:41:42,310 --> 00:41:43,670
I said something wrong again.

626
00:41:43,670 --> 00:41:45,092
Don't cry... Alright...

627
00:41:45,092 --> 00:41:47,130
I'm sorry... Don't cry...

628
